SECTION 1. The following places and sitios in the Municipality of Casiguran, Province of Sorsogon, are declared as barrios thereof, to wit:

The sitios of Cabognahan, Cagdagat, Fabrica, Lubas and Marines, as a distinct and independent barrio to be known as the barrio of Boton;

The sitios of Mambot and Namuut, as a distinct and independent barrio to be known as the barrio of Burgos;

The barrio of Casay as barrio Casay;

The barrio of Cogon as barrio Cogon;

The barrio of Inlagadean as barrio Inlagadean;

The barrio of Lugñid as barrio Lugñid;

The barrio of Mabini as barrio Mabini;

The sitio of Pamakiran as a barrio to be known as the barrio of Ponong;

sitios of Colambis, Lugi, Malagomgom, Rawag and Tiris, as a distinct and independent barrio to be known as the barrio of Rizal;

The barrio of San Antonio as barrio San Antonio;

The sitios of Tigbao and Nabugñaren, as a distinct and independent barrio to be known as the barrio of San Isidro

The sitio of Escuela, as a barrio to be known as the barrio of San Juan;

The sitios of Cadiang and Purog, as a distinct and independent barrio to be known as the barrio of Pascual;

The sitios of Cadiang and Purog, as a distinct and independent barrio to be known as the barrio of Pascual;

The sitios of Buraburan, Calayogan, Sog-ong Talahib, as a distinct and independent barrio to be known as the barrio of Santa Cruz;

The sitios of Mauhang and Storeroom, as a distinct and independent barrio to be known as the barrio of Trece Martires; and

The sitios of Adovis, Busing, Cawit, Central, Somalot, Timbayog, Tinampo and Tulay, as a distinct and independent barrio to be known as the barrio of Poblacion.
